g.ns16:text: \\centering\n{\\bf \\large DMFT} represents\\\\\nexcursions from a site into the\\\\\ncorrelated bath in the form of \\\\\nself-energies for the bath and\\\\\nthe impurity. This results\\\\\nin a three-peak DOS\\\\\nof the bath.

\\centering\nThe {\\bf \\large extended\\\\\nSIAM} represents these\\\\\nexcursions by generating\\\\\ninteractions $J$ and $U_b$. These\\\\\ninteractions mimick the effect\\\\\nof the impurity and bath\\\\\nself-energies as observed\\\\\nwithin DMFT.
